that's where you're needed.

16
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:36,230
﻿"that's where you have to go."
I liked that.

17
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:41,510
﻿I said: If that's the best part of
the job. then that's what I want.

18
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:48,590
