﻿The first thing I remember
is my overlapping week.

33
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:39,670
﻿We met the medical team
that serves there.

34
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,470
﻿We said hello.
I introduced myself.

35
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:48,750
﻿Next thing I remember
is hearing over the radio

36
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:54,190
﻿in the ambulance beside us:
"Man down in Noga 9.

37
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,670
﻿"man down in Noga 9."

38
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,710
﻿Before I knew it.
I was told that

39
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:07,190
