40
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:11,510
﻿The medic ran first
and I ran after him.

41
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:16,150
﻿When I reached the door,
they yelled at me to duck.

42
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:19,950
﻿I did what everyone else did.
