no bullets would hit us.

47
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:41,830
﻿We drove back to
the infirmary at HQ.

48
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,670
﻿The doctor came,
shook my hand and said:

49
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:48,030
﻿"Congratulations,
that was your first incident.

50
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,310
﻿"That's how you learn."

51
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:56,190
