currently on the Bar artery.

53
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,070
﻿They're definitely
up to something.

54
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,790
﻿Vertex to Snow White.

55
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:32,110
﻿They're heading towards
the far end of the Bar artery.

56
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:39,110
﻿Roger. I'm going there on foot.
I'll get to them on foot.

57
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,830
﻿It's loads of power.

58
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:48,550
﻿There's an incident
that's about to happen

59
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,190
﻿and it'll happen
the way you make it happen.

60
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:57,510
﻿You hear soldiers
panting over the radio,

61
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,550
﻿because you're making them run.

62
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,390
﻿they're running
because you said so.

63
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,830
﻿The commander radios in
